						<summary>

						<p><hi rend="bold">Chōḻa, Parakēśarivarman, Year 12 = c. 10th century.</hi></p>						

						<p>This is much damaged. It seems to record some endowment made by one Raṇamuka-Nāraṇan, for feeding Brahmanas (in the temple on the hill) on the day of his natal star Rohini in the Masi month.</p>						

						<p>[Published in <hi rend="italic">SII</hi> Vol. XIX No. 299.]</p>						

